WEBVTT

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:24.359
ظآزThe whole world is lit upظآز

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:25.979
ظآزBecause you existظآز

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:28.019
ظآزYou're alwaysظآز

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:32.679
ظآزSomewhere close, flying with meظآز

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.299
ظآزGo to where the wind blowsظآز

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.019
ظآزHold tightظآز

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:42.879
ظآزTo the ray of light that belongs to usظآز

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:47.400
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 4=

00:00:50.740 --> 00:00:53.010
Such an important exhibit was stolen,

00:00:53.050 --> 00:00:55.009
yet the group's alarm didn't go off.

00:00:55.010 --> 00:00:58.060
And it happened right before
the exhibition was about to start.

00:00:59.370 --> 00:01:00.780
Don't you find it strange?

00:01:04.130 --> 00:01:05.290
What are you trying to say?

00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:07.570
I just want to know.

00:01:07.660 --> 00:01:10.689
As the new
Head of Security for Mu Group,

00:01:10.690 --> 00:01:12.209
what do you think

00:01:12.210 --> 00:01:13.220
about this theft?

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.620
What do I think?

00:01:16.660 --> 00:01:19.769
I spent all of yesterday playing house

00:01:19.770 --> 00:01:21.060
with a certain lady.

00:01:21.610 --> 00:01:23.609
How would I have time
to worry about the theft?

00:01:23.610 --> 00:01:24.370
I...

00:01:40.970 --> 00:01:42.340
Shen Jibai.

00:01:43.050 --> 00:01:44.140
Shen Jibai.

00:01:45.250 --> 00:01:46.340
Shen Jibai,

00:01:46.380 --> 00:01:47.450
are you there?

00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:49.420
Shen Jibai, are you there?

00:01:52.740 --> 00:01:54.290
The door to
the collection room is locked.

00:01:54.900 --> 00:01:56.450
The airtightness here is excellent.

00:01:57.100 --> 00:01:59.120
The longer we're here,
the thinner the oxygen will get.

00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:01.000
We have to find a way out
as soon as possible.

00:02:11.020 --> 00:02:12.020
What's wrong?

00:02:27.650 --> 00:02:29.060
I have night blindness.

00:02:29.770 --> 00:02:31.899
I can't see anything in the dark.

00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:32.740
So...

00:02:38.820 --> 00:02:40.659
ظآزCircling repeatedlyظآز

00:02:40.660 --> 00:02:42.399
ظآزLike a flight with no destinationظآز

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:44.560
ظآزIf longing can be foldedظآز

00:02:45.770 --> 00:02:46.970
Is this a bit better?

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:53.589
ظآزWhere is the edge of the dream?ظآز

00:02:53.590 --> 00:02:57.139
ظآزAlways measuring the interval
between breath and silenceظآز

00:02:57.140 --> 00:03:00.719
ظآزLike fishing
for raindrops in the desertظآز

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:04.690
ظآزIf time stopped spinningظآز

00:03:05.430 --> 00:03:08.259
ظآزOur passion would expireظآز

00:03:08.260 --> 00:03:11.459
ظآزIf my heart refuses
to compromise with the nightظآز

00:03:11.460 --> 00:03:14.049
ظآزI'll tear out my ribs
to strike the stars louderظآز

00:03:14.050 --> 00:03:15.259
Just point the light anywhere.

00:03:15.260 --> 00:03:18.410
ظآزSettling in my veinsظآز

00:03:19.350 --> 00:03:24.900
ظآزEvery flutterظآز

00:03:33.180 --> 00:03:34.090
Wait a second.

00:03:40.420 --> 00:03:42.810
Why is this display case
different from the others?

00:03:43.210 --> 00:03:44.780
This one is recessed.

00:03:45.260 --> 00:03:47.329
This is a gravity-sensing system

00:03:47.330 --> 00:03:49.180
specifically set up
for high-profile exhibits.

00:03:49.930 --> 00:03:52.579
Once the collection item is removed,
it triggers an alarm.

00:03:52.580 --> 00:03:54.930
It can only be bypassed
using a special chip device.

00:03:55.330 --> 00:03:56.250
These thieves

00:03:56.370 --> 00:03:57.250
are very professional.

00:03:57.700 --> 00:03:58.929
If the alarm goes off,

00:03:58.930 --> 00:04:01.090
the group's security personnel
will arrive immediately.

00:04:01.980 --> 00:04:03.419
But the Han Dynasty White Jade Bowl

00:04:03.420 --> 00:04:05.130
did indeed vanish quietly.

00:04:05.740 --> 00:04:06.530
Right.

00:04:06.610 --> 00:04:07.930
As long as the alarm sounds,

00:04:08.020 --> 00:04:09.580
the security personnel will come.

00:04:09.980 --> 00:04:11.460
I know how we can get out.

00:04:14.260 --> 00:04:15.580
What are you doing?

00:04:24.620 --> 00:04:25.260
Hello?

00:04:27.970 --> 00:04:29.529
Mr. He, I'm so sorry.

00:04:29.530 --> 00:04:30.760
Director Mu is busy right now,

00:04:30.760 --> 00:04:32.280
so it might not
be convenient to see you.

00:04:32.380 --> 00:04:33.260
It's fine.

00:04:33.460 --> 00:04:34.440
I'll leave the item here.

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:36.139
She can just
come pick it up when she's free.

00:04:36.140 --> 00:04:36.700
Alright.

00:04:38.090 --> 00:04:38.819
What?

00:04:38.820 --> 00:04:40.820
Director Mu is locked
in the collection room?

00:04:43.410 --> 00:04:44.410
Yu.

00:04:48.330 --> 00:04:49.460
What's going on?

00:04:49.700 --> 00:04:51.410
Why did the alarm go off out of nowhere?

00:04:51.700 --> 00:04:52.780
Ms. Xu,

00:04:53.140 --> 00:04:55.700
is there a major problem
with your company's security system?

00:04:55.700 --> 00:04:57.800
Why would someone
be locked inside and unable to get out?

00:04:59.210 --> 00:05:01.340
I don't follow you, Mr. He.

00:05:01.460 --> 00:05:03.089
Since when is it an outsider's place

00:05:03.090 --> 00:05:05.650
to tell us how
to run our security at Mu Group?

00:05:06.330 --> 00:05:07.580
Open the door for me.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:09.680
(Collection Room)

00:05:27.460 --> 00:05:28.209
Zhiyu,

00:05:28.210 --> 00:05:29.380
are you okay?

00:05:30.290 --> 00:05:31.970
I was so afraid you were hurt.

00:05:32.380 --> 00:05:34.260
Thank goodness,
Jibai was there to protect you.

00:05:34.500 --> 00:05:35.019
Otherwise,

00:05:35.020 --> 00:05:37.090
if you got hurt,
I wouldn't know how to explain it.

00:05:38.330 --> 00:05:39.650
Look, Mr. He,

00:05:40.260 --> 00:05:42.820
isn't Zhiyu
being well-protected by Jibai?

00:05:43.020 --> 00:05:44.580
This is much better

00:05:44.620 --> 00:05:46.059
than us worrying out here.

00:05:46.060 --> 00:05:47.090
Don't worry.

00:05:47.290 --> 00:05:48.460
We're fine.

00:05:48.530 --> 00:05:51.780
It's thanks to Shen Jibai's
familiarity with the security system.

00:05:52.210 --> 00:05:53.290
However,

00:05:53.500 --> 00:05:56.650
we've managed to find
key evidence regarding the theft.

00:05:57.260 --> 00:05:58.780
To be safe,

00:05:59.020 --> 00:06:01.610
it's best to hand the case
over to the police immediately

00:06:01.700 --> 00:06:02.900
and seal off the scene.

00:06:24.330 --> 00:06:26.900
Ms. Xu, is something
the matter so late at night?

00:06:27.410 --> 00:06:29.340
How are your injuries from today?

00:06:32.380 --> 00:06:32.939
Take this.

00:06:32.940 --> 00:06:34.140
Have a drink with me.

00:06:37.060 --> 00:06:37.969
I hadn't noticed before

00:06:37.970 --> 00:06:39.610
that you were such a gentleman.

00:06:40.210 --> 00:06:41.940
It's just a minor scratch. It's nothing.

00:06:42.580 --> 00:06:44.820
Do you remember what I told you to do?

00:06:45.650 --> 00:06:48.020
If I don't get what I want,

00:06:48.140 --> 00:06:50.140
I won't pay a single cent.

00:06:50.640 --> 00:06:51.540
I...

00:06:52.060 --> 00:06:53.260
Shen Jibai.

00:06:58.170 --> 00:06:59.260
Shen Jibai.

00:07:05.730 --> 00:07:06.780
Is something wrong?

00:07:07.020 --> 00:07:09.050
Are your injuries okay?

00:07:09.260 --> 00:07:10.050
I'm fine.

00:07:20.770 --> 00:07:22.139
Drinking while you're injured?

00:07:22.140 --> 00:07:23.780
The wound will get inflamed.

00:07:24.330 --> 00:07:26.220
Don't tell me you lack
even this much common sense.

00:07:34.900 --> 00:07:36.260
Is this really necessary?

00:07:55.410 --> 00:07:56.610
When I was little,

00:07:56.700 --> 00:07:58.220
my mom used to say

00:07:58.620 --> 00:08:00.970
that wounds must be disinfected
after an injury.

00:08:04.020 --> 00:08:06.059
ظآزThe fragmented, peacefulظآز

00:08:06.060 --> 00:08:08.419
ظآزTiniest dreamظآز

00:08:08.420 --> 00:08:10.269
ظآزSlips through the window by chanceظآز

00:08:10.270 --> 00:08:12.529
ظآزShines into my lifeظآز

00:08:12.530 --> 00:08:15.070
ظآزYou never say a wordظآز

00:08:15.260 --> 00:08:17.410
You're quite skilled at this.
Have you learned it before?

00:08:18.380 --> 00:08:19.619
When I was abroad,

00:08:19.620 --> 00:08:21.170
I took veterinary medicine
as an elective.

00:08:21.210 --> 00:08:22.850
I've bandaged a lot of animals.

00:08:23.150 --> 00:08:25.169
ظآزMy world becomes hazyظآز

00:08:25.170 --> 00:08:27.059
ظآزAdvancing while retreatingظآز

00:08:27.060 --> 00:08:28.850
I've always been curious.

00:08:29.770 --> 00:08:30.969
With your skills

00:08:30.970 --> 00:08:32.580
and strong professional abilities,

00:08:33.050 --> 00:08:33.929
how can you be content

00:08:33.930 --> 00:08:34.929
with being just a lowly

00:08:34.930 --> 00:08:36.649
Head of Security at our Mu Group?

00:08:36.650 --> 00:08:38.090
Or could it be...

00:08:39.980 --> 00:08:41.460
Are you following my stepmom

00:08:41.650 --> 00:08:42.820
and planning to move up?

00:08:42.980 --> 00:08:45.320
The terms Mu Group
offers for a Head of Security

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:47.520
are enough for an average person
to work for many years.

00:08:47.520 --> 00:08:49.700
ظآزNot daring to say too muchظآز

00:08:51.260 --> 00:08:53.090
The money at Mu Group

00:08:53.740 --> 00:08:54.940
isn't that easy to earn.

00:08:57.530 --> 00:09:00.220
As long as you can cause me less trouble

00:09:00.290 --> 00:09:02.480
and not stir up so many things,
it'll be fine, Miss Mu.

00:09:03.140 --> 00:09:06.279
ظآزNot daring to say too muchظآز

00:09:06.280 --> 00:09:12.190
ظآزPerhaps you already
understand my heartظآز

00:09:19.340 --> 00:09:20.139
The medicine spilled.

00:09:20.140 --> 00:09:21.370
I'll go get a towel.

00:09:33.670 --> 00:09:37.900
ظآزLight comes beaming inظآز

00:09:38.040 --> 00:09:42.409
ظآزLanding on my skinظآز

00:09:42.410 --> 00:09:46.900
ظآزWarms the space you left behindظآز

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:55.380
ظآزShadows move aroundظآز

00:09:55.470 --> 00:09:59.669
ظآزAwake, racing thoughtsظآز

00:09:59.670 --> 00:10:04.200
ظآزTry to keep the memories safeظآز

00:10:07.800 --> 00:10:13.590
ظآزDon't slip awayظآز

00:10:16.040 --> 00:10:20.609
ظآزI'm all yours, all yoursظآز

00:10:20.610 --> 00:10:25.009
ظآزI'm all yours, all yoursظآز

