ظآزI'm all yours, all yoursظآز

00:10:29.350 --> 00:10:33.330
ظآزI'm all yours, all yoursظآز

00:10:33.800 --> 00:10:38.109
ظآزI'm all yours, all yoursظآز

00:10:38.110 --> 00:10:42.439
ظآزI'm all yours, all yoursظآز

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:46.749
ظآزI'm all yours, all yoursظآز

00:10:46.750 --> 00:10:52.900
ظآزI'm all yours, all yoursظآز